Brodi Phoenix - "Lemon Drop"

From San Antonio to Dallas, Brodi Phoenix is reshaping Hip-Hop with a dynamic blend of R&B, Soul, and Funk. Merging the raw lyricism and delivery of '90s Hip-Hop, the smoothness of 2000s R&B, and a modern touch, he brings a fresh perspective as both an artist and producer. Artist Of The Month Quita D

Quita D, the talented female music artist born in the vibrant city of Savannah, GA, draws inspiration from musical powerhouses such as Trina, Nicki Minaj, Missy Elliott, and Lil' Kim. With a burning passion for music ignited by these influential artists, Quita D embarked on her journey as a singer-songwriter at a young age.
